originalText.text: I recently had the pleasure of working with Nikki as part of a client activation and was absolutely blown away by her expertise and skillset. Her unique perspective on the wellness industry and integrative health space is unparalleled and I encourage anyone seeking these services to inquire about her offerings. Alongside my client, I invited top-tier editors in the lifestyle, beauty, and fitness space to join Nikki for a private Ear Seeding experience, one of her signature practices. Both my client and the media were so appreciative of the time and attention Nikki took to create an intimate session that left us all feeling refreshed and informed. Nikki's passion for her work and commitment to serving others makes her an asset to anyone looking for health and wellness services to better themselves, their team, or loved ones. I'm looking forward to staying in touch with her and finding ways to incorporate her offerings into my routine, both personally and professionally.

I’ve been working with Nikki for quite some time now and I felt compelled to write a review, bc she is so deserving!

I am constantly amazed by all the tools Nikki has in her toolbox. Just when I think I have an insurmountable issue, Nikki is able to be an incredible sounding board, hold space, but even further, she offers solutions I could never have come up with on my own.

I did the food sensitivity and omg, the insights!! It was truly life changing!!

This journey can be tough sometimes but having Nikki as a partner, makes me feel like I can do anything!!

Choosing Nikki was the best gift I ever gave myself!

originalText.text: Working with Nikki has changed my life. Physically, I feel like a new person with a healthy, smart food plan that works for me. I finally understand and appreciate what I put into my body. And I understand what my body needs, as well as can't tolerate based on the ALCAT food intolerance test. Emotionally, I finally have someone I can speak to honestly without judgment about the variety of food and health of issues I have experienced throughout life. Her nonstop support and encouragement, in a way that works for me, has made a huge difference. When I first went to Nikki, I had been diagnosed with a mild case of colitis. Thanks to her nutrition plan, I have been able to keep it in check without having to go on medication. I also lost 10 pounds in the process without counting a single calorie! Nikki is one of a kind and I can't recommend her strongly enough to anyone who wants to eat well and feel their best!
